data.description: NEW PRICE!!   Bring your paint brushes and pick out some flooring and have plenty of room for future upgrades at this price!  There's so much going for this 4 BDRM RANCH, 3 CAR, 3 FULL BATH, finished walk out home!  TWO kitchens, cul-de-sac .34 acre lot with double gated, 6ft privacy fenced back yard and good sized shed!  Main floor laundry right off kitchen with 2nd laundry in lower level!  Walk out from dining room to back deck that stretches all the way across the house (patio underneath), deck entrance from Master as well. Master has jetted tub, dbl vanity, 10x9 walk in closet! Great room has vaulted ceilings, cozy fireplace and loads of natural light! Downstairs has 2nd kitchen w/ island, double sink, built in micro, stove and fridge, 2 bdrms, pantry, 2nd laundry room and full bath! Generous room sizes and lots of walk in closets!  Flooring and some fresh paint will go a long way for some instant equity!  Great bones!  Located in Blue Springs South HS district, Daniel Young Elementary and Moreland Ridge Middle, just west of 7 Hwy and Mooreland School Rd.  No HOA!
